uk.co.bluegumtree.code.java.goodreads.organiser.controller
Class GoodreadsDataOrganiser

java.lang.Object
  uk.co.bluegumtree.code.java.goodreads.organiser.controller.GoodreadsDataOrganiser

public class GoodreadsDataOrganiser
extends java.lang.Object

Processes data collected for use with the Book Recommender. Merges data from multiple sources, splits review lists up into individual review files, filters out reviews/books that can't be positively identified as fiction and divides each user's library into two sets: testing and training.

Author:
Sheila Ellen Thomson
